# VulkanDesktop — test & smoke-run CLI

Full reference: [`Docs/CLI.md`](Docs/CLI.md). Implementation: `VulkanDesktop/Util/Util_EngineConfig.cpp`.

**Binary:** `x64\Debug\VulkanDesktop.exe` (after `MSBuild VulkanDesktop.sln /p:Configuration=Debug /p:Platform=x64`).

**Log:** `Logs/engine_runtime_log.txt` (repo root; fresh each run).

---

## When to use which command

| Goal | Command |
|------|---------|
| CLI parses, no GPU | `.\VulkanDesktop.exe --help` |
| Default demo scene, quick visual (~4s then kill) | See **Background smoke** below |
| Full lifecycle (UnloadScene + Shutdown), automated exit | **Graceful smoke** (preferred for task close) |
| Minimal asset closure | `--scene Data/Scenes/smoke.json` |
| Scene-load / manifest / asset path work | `--scene …` + optional `--asset-root <repo-root>` from non-root cwd |
| Avoid validation-layer install failures on CI/agent | add `--no-validation` |
| ImGui Scene panel / in-process reload | Run default; switch scenes in **Scene** window (no extra CLI) |

---

## Graceful smoke (preferred for vibe-coding verification)

After **`LoadSceneResources`**, runs the main loop for at least **6 seconds** (default scene from config), then closes and executes `UnloadScene` → `Shutdown`. Record exit code **0** and log lines in `_Progress.md`.

From `x64\Debug` (asset root auto-detected; default `Data/Scenes/demo.json`):

```powershell
Set-Location x64\Debug
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --no-validation --smoke-seconds 6
```

**Demo scene** (9 entities, explicit path):

```powershell
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --no-validation --smoke-seconds 6 --scene Data/Scenes/demo.json
```

**Smoke scene** (1 entity, faster load; still dwell 6s):

```powershell
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --no-validation --smoke-seconds 6 --scene Data/Scenes/smoke.json
```

**Explicit asset root** (any cwd):

```powershell
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --asset-root D:\Code\SiriusEngine_VulkanReboot --no-validation --smoke-seconds 6 --scene Data/Scenes/smoke.json
```

**Fast CI path** (minimal dwell; exits after **n** frames — use only when 6s wait is unnecessary):

```powershell
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --no-validation --smoke-frames 2
```

If both `--smoke-seconds` and `--smoke-frames` are set, **both** thresholds must be met before exit.

### Success signals (tail `Logs/engine_runtime_log.txt`)

- `[CONFIG] assetRoot=…` under repo
- `[SCENE] LoadSceneResources completed`
- `[EXTRACT]` / `[RESOURCE-TABLE]` / `FillInstanceSlab` (counts match scene)
- `[APP] Smoke dwell:` / `[APP] Smoke dwell reached (6s)`
- `[SCENE] UnloadScene: GPU scene resources released`
- `[APP] Engine exited run loop normally`
- No crash/assert after `Shutdown`; process exit code **0**
- No new `[ERROR]` on init path (validation missing is OK if `--no-validation`)

